{"tid":1078322,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇維峯·浚匯","createTime":"2019-03-26T08:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T20:04:49.000Z","uid":178584,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3d63df47cc5c23001b96985829c3afd44994d9","tid":1078322,"uid":178584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:17:11.000Z","msg":"維峯&middot;浚匯首批50伙 折實入場498萬餘起<br />\n<br />\n市況回順,多個新盤趕緊推售,其中北角維峯&middot;浚匯首張價單推出50伙，包括38伙一房及12伙開放式戶，折實呎價23,752至29,212元，折實入場費逾498萬元起。恒基物業代理營業(二)部總經理韓家輝表示，當中12伙可承做九成按揭。<br />\n<br />\n韓氏指首批開價貼近同區一、二手做價，加推具加價空間，料下周開售。示範單位今起開放，明日起收票。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣樓, 唔駛5球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e3f28e2bcf992bde700b1b7bace7fec30e671f","tid":1078322,"uid":37358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"入門得個百幾呎<br />\n點住得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a28ad3ea609d0aa3047940e0acb8f2f2e29182","tid":1078322,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"預計首輪開價單位不少於50伙，並將提供高成數按揭，而項目管理費為每呎4.56元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，是次開放的單位為趟門設計，項目所有B室及B室均採用趟門設計，合共涉及48戶。項目提供216伙，間隔包括開放式及1房戶，實用面積175至302平方呎，預計關鍵日期為2020年8月31日。"},{"pid":"f616946e92942e5dccdd15a8a8a375a29e0954b9","tid":1078322,"uid":90119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:18:27.000Z","msg":"個位係靚，但如果我有六球幾既都揀到港島其他非新樓啦"},{"pid":"8044c4b2a9eab2a0b9587d4da3849fe4cd16716a","tid":1078322,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"就黎起好咁滯"},{"pid":"63c9147b56d934854b9731f464f70729128ec280","tid":1078322,"uid":209853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母首張價單都25000/呎？<br />\n貨尾可能40000/呎<br />\n有無咁撚狂<br />\n恆基樓有咩咁好可以咁高溢價？"},{"pid":"07bf11285fe6924fcd52fb1cce31d9dfc87ad0df","tid":1078322,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180703/large/1530601815_d514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180703%2Flarge%2F1530601815_d514.jpg&h=656d734f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMILF"},{"pid":"ee3ad7f45eb628284981bd69f680591a251fdd67","tid":1078322,"uid":219432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"如非必要，唔好再買納米樓，一來呎價絕不平，二來防守力極差，最後千萬唔好貪發展商２按(以為一定借)，否則好易計錯數，蝕咗訂金就真係喊都無謂。"},{"pid":"1c6db8c4316b570e46f22bc0b1f4e4c42810771a","tid":1078322,"uid":228794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"開放式應該會收儉 ，但一房應該值錢"},{"pid":"c2327a41ec1a25ffce8049f160afdeab698f82aa","tid":1078322,"uid":5627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"200呎500萬起係咩玩法<br />\n開放式租唔租到萬4蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdea3e38f05f5b752e005f388a112d862854a813","tid":1078322,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2327a41ec1a25ffce8049f160afdeab698f82aa","tid":1078322,"uid":5627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"200呎500萬起係咩玩法<br />\n開放式租唔租到萬4蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"參考<br />\n<br />\n北角尚譽錄3宗租務成交，其中一宗開放式呎租達93元。美聯助理區域經理余迅力表示，上述租務成交單位為高層D室，實用面積167平方呎，採開放式間隔，以每月租金1.55萬元租出，實用呎租達93元，料創港島東呎租新高。"},{"pid":"a7d215f9471d4d644e42d3d2f0b2b4af0c3e4f29","tid":1078322,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdea3e38f05f5b752e005f388a112d862854a813","tid":1078322,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2327a41ec1a25ffce8049f160afdeab698f82aa","tid":1078322,"uid":5627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T11:06:31.00